text: "No Secrets" is a 1980 song by Australian rock band The Angels. It is the leading single from their fourth studio album Dark Room and went to number 8 in Australia. ==Track listing== Epic Records ES 417 # "No Secrets" (Graham Bidstrup, Doc Neeson) \- 4:17 # "Staring Voices" (Doc Neeson, John Brewster, Rick Brewster, Graham Buzz" Bidstrup) - 2:39 ==References== Category:1980 songs Category:Hard rock songs Category:The Angels (Australian band) songs
title: No Secrets (song)
